u306f\u30d7\u30ea\u30ad\u30e5\u30a2 \u30aa\u30fc\u30eb\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u30ba\u30e1\u30e2\u30ea\u30fc\u30ba|Eiga Hagutto! Purikyua \u2661 Futari wa Puri Kyua \u014cru Sut\u0101zu Memor\u012bzu}}\n|October 27, 2018\n|-\n|12\n|{{nihongo|''[[Pretty Cure Miracle Universe]]''|\u6620\u753b \u30d7\u30ea\u30ad\u30e5\u30a2\u30df\u30e9\u30af\u30eb\u30e6\u30cb\u30d0\u30fc\u30b9|Eiga Purikyua Mirakuru Yunib\u0101su}}\n|March 16, 2019\n|-\n|13\n|{{nihongo|''[[Pretty Cure All Stars#Pretty Cure Miracle Leap: A Wonderful Day with Everyone|Pretty Cure Miracle Leap: A Wonderful Day with Everyone]]''|\u6620\u753b\u30d7\u30ea\u30ad\u30e5\u30a2\u30df\u30e9\u30af\u30eb\u30ea\u30fc\u30d7 \u307f\u3093\u306a\u3068\u306e\u4e0d\u601d\u8b70\u306a1\u65e5|Eiga Purikyua Mirakuru R\u012bpu Min'na to no Fushigi na 1 Nichi}}\n|May 16, 2020\n|}\n\n== Box office performance ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+\n!Rank\n!Title\n!Year\n!Box office gross\n!Ref\n|-\n|1\n|''[[Pretty Cure All Stars DX2: Light of Hope - Protect the Rainbow Jewel!]]''\n|2010\n|$14,412,834\n|<ref>{{cite web |title=2010 |url=http://www.eiren.org/boxoffice_e/2010.html |website=Eiren |publisher=[[:ja:\u65e5\u672c\u6620\u753b\u88fd\u4f5c\u8005\u9023\u76df|Motion Picture Producers Association of Japan]] |accessdate=18 February 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|2\n|''[[Pretty Cure All Stars New Stage: Friends of the Future]]''\n|2012\n|$12,783,557\n|<ref>{{cite web |title=2012 |url=http://www.eiren.org/boxoffice_e/2012.html |website=Eiren |publisher=[[:ja:\u65e5\u672c\u6620\u753b\u88fd\u4f5c\u8005\u9023\u76df|Motion Picture Producers Association of Japan]] |accessdate=18 February 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|3\n|''[[Pretty Cure All Stars DX3: Deliver the Future! The Rainbow-Colored Flower That Connects the World]]''\n|2011\n|$12,780,834\n|<ref>{{cite web |title=2011 |url=http://www.eiren.org/boxoffice_e/2011.html |website=Eiren |publisher=[[:ja:\u65e5\u672c\u6620\u753b\u88fd\u4f5c\u8005\u9023\u76df|Motion Picture Producers Association of Japan]] |accessd