sfn|Fellgiebel|2000|p=40}}\n*[[Order of Merit of the Federal Republic of Germany|Commander's Cross of the Order of Merit of the Federal Republic of Germany]] (19 September 1969){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=143}}\n\n===Promotions===\n{| style=\"background: transparent;\"\n! Kriegsmarine\n|-\n| 1 July 1935: || ''[[F\u00e4hnrich zur See]]'' (Officer Cadet){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=141}}\n|-\n| 1 April 1937: || ''[[Leutnant zur See]]'' (Second Lieutenant){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=141}}\n|-\n| 1 April 1939: || ''[[Oberleutnant zur See]]'' (First Lieutenant){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=142}}\n|-\n| 1 September 1941: || ''[[Kapit\u00e4nleutnant]]'' (Captain Lieutenant){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=142}}\n|-\n| 17 August 1942: || ''[[Korvettenkapit\u00e4n]]'' (Corvette Captain){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=142}}\n|-\n| 1 December 1944: || ''[[Fregattenkapit\u00e4n]]'' (Frigate Captain){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=142}}\n|-\n! Bundesmarine\n|-\n| 1 November 1959: || ''[[Kapit\u00e4n zur See]]'' (Captain at Sea){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=143}}\n|-\n| 15 November 1966: || ''[[Flottillenadmiral]]'' (Flotilla Admiral){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=143}}\n|-\n| 21 December 1966: || ''[[Konteradmiral]]'' (Counter Admiral){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=143}}\n|}\n\n==Translation notes==\n{{Reflist|group=\"Tr\"|30em}}\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist|group=\"Note\"}}\n\n==References==\n\n===Citations===\n{{Reflist|25em}}\n\n===Bibliography===\n{{Refbegin|30em}}\n* {{cite book\n  |last=Ben-Yehuda\n  |first=Nachman\n  |authorlink=Nachman Ben-Yehuda\n  |title=Atrocity, Deviance, and Submarine Warfare: Norms and Practices During the World Wars\n  |publisher=[[Michigan University]]\n  |year=2016\n  |isbn=978-0-472-11889-2\n  |ref=harv\n}}\n* {{cite book\n  |last=Blair\n  |first=Clay\n  |authorlink=Clay Blair\n  |title=Hitler's U-Boat War: The Hunters, 1939\u20131942\n  |publisher=Random House\n  |year=1998\n  |isbn=978-0-30787-437-5\n  |ref=harv\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n  |last=Bridgland\n  |first=Tony\n  |year=2001\n  |title=Waves of Hate: Naval Atrocities of the Second World War\n  |url=https://books.google.de/books?id=fwmSAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA216&dq=David+H.+Atwater\n  |location=\n  |publisher=Pen and Sword\n  |isbn=978-1-4738-2061-6\n  |ref=harv\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n  |last1=Busch\n  |first1=Rainer\n  |last2=R\u00f6ll\n  |first2=Hans-Joachim\n  |year=2003\n  |title=Der U-Boot-Krieg 1939\u20131945 \u2014 Die Ritterkreuztr\u00e4ger der U-Boot-Waffe von September 1939 bis Mai 1945\n  |trans-title=The U-Boat War 1939\u20131945 \u2014 The Knight's Cross Bearers of the U-Boat Force from September 1939 to May 1945\n  |language=German\n  |location=Hamburg, Berlin, Bonn Germany\n  |publisher=Verlag E.S. Mittler & Sohn\n  |isbn=978-3-8132-0515-2\n  |ref=harv\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n  |last=Edwards\n  |first=Bernard\n  |title=The Twilight of the U-boats\n  |date=2004\n  |publisher=[[Naval Institute Press]]\n  |isbn=978-1844150359\n  |ref=harv\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n  |last=Fellgiebel\n  |first=Walther-Peer\n  |authorlink=Walther-Peer Fellgiebel\n  |year=2000\n  |origyear=1986\n  |title=Die Tr\u00e4ger des Ritterkreuzes des Eisernen Kreuzes 1939\u20131945 \u2014 Die Inhaber der h\u00f6chsten Auszeichnung des Zweiten Weltkrieges aller Wehrmachtteile\n  |trans-title=The Bearers of the Knight's Cross of the Iron Cross 1939\u20131945 \u2014 The Owners of the Highest Award of the Second World War of all Wehrmacht Branches\n  |language=German\n  |location=Friedberg, Germany\n  |publisher=Podzun-Pallas\n  |isbn=978-3-7909-0284-6\n  |ref=harv\n}}\n* {{cite book\n  |last=Gablik\n  |first=Axel F.\n  |year=1996\n  |title=Strategische Planungen in der Bundesrepublik Deutschland 1955\u20131967: Politische Kontrolle oder milit\u00e4rische Notwendigkeit?\n  |trans-title=Strategic Planing in the Federal Republic of Germany 1955\u20131967: Political Control or Military Necessity?\n  |language=German\n  |location=Baden-Baden, Germany\n  |publisher=Nomos\n  |isbn=978-3-7890-4255-3\n  |ref=harv\n}}\n* 