 Best Ever Award''.{{cn|date=January 2020}}\n*2015 [[Forbes]], Ranked \"Number One\" as The World's Highest-Paid Celebrities.<ref>{{cite web|title = Floyd Mayweather, Manny Pacquiao, Katy Perry and One Direction top this year's Celebrity 100 list\u2014the first truly global ranking of the highest paid entertainers on the planet|url = https://www.forbes.com/celebrities/list/#tab:overall|website = Forbes|accessdate = October 22, 2015}}</ref>\n*2015 [[Edward J. Neil Trophy|Boxing Writers Association of America Fighter of the Year]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/boxing/story/_/id/14726413/floyd-mayweather-wins-sugar-ray-robinson-fighter-year-award-third |title=Floyd Mayweather wins Sugar Ray Robinson Fighter of the Year award for third time |website=Espn.go.com |date=February 8, 2016 |accessdate=December 27, 2016}}</ref>\n*2016 [[Guinness World Records]] Most bouts undefeated by a world champion boxer in a career (49)\n*2016 [[Guinness World Records]] Highest career [[pay-per-view]] sales for a boxer ($1.3 billion)\n*2016 [[Guinness World Records]] Most expensive boxing championship belt ($1 Million)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxingscene.com/photos-mayweather-golovkin-klitschko-wbc-convention--111729 |title=Photos: Mayweather, Golovkin, Klitschko at WBC Convention \u2013 Boxing News |website=Boxingscene.com |date= |accessdate=December 27, 2016}}</ref>\n{{div col end}}\n\n* 2018 Forbes magazine #1 of the world's 100 highest paid entertainers<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/forbespr/2018/07/16/forbes-releases-2018-celebrity-100-list-of-the-worlds-highest-paid-entertainers/#7710538923b5|title=Forbes Releases 2018 Celebrity 100 List Of The World's Highest-Paid Entertainers|last=Communications|first=Forbes Corporate|work=Forbes|access-date=July 17, 2018|language=en}}</ref>\n\n*2019 Forbes magazine highest paid athlete of the decade\n\n*2010 - 2019 [[Boxing Writers Association of America]] Fighter of the Decade\n\n*2010 - 2019 [[World Boxing Assoc